算结果\n- `cache_dir`：`~/.claude/analyses/<project_key>/`（绝对路径，以 `/` 结尾）\n- `overwrite_index_entry`：若传了 `--reanalyze` 则为 `true`，否则为 `false`\n\n## 约束\n\n- 不修改目标项目任何文件\n- 分析结果只写入 `~/.claude/analyses/`\n- 激活门控和前置检查失败时立即停止，不继续执行\n```\n\n## Steps\n\n1. Check that `/Users/xpeng/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/commands/` directory exists.\n2. Write the file with the exact content above.\n3. Verify: `head -6 /Users/xpeng/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/commands/diagnose.md` to confirm frontmatter.\n4. Verify file exists: `ls /Users/xpeng/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/commands/diagnose.md`\n\n## Important Notes\n\n- Pure Markdown file — no code to run.\n- Triple-backtick code fences within the content are literal documentation examples.\n- Do NOT modify any existing files.\n\n## Status Reporting\n\nReport **DONE**, **DONE_WITH_CONCERNS**, or **BLOCKED**."},"uuid":"df8d949c-d5d4-4d5d-b9d5-9dff9803781f","timestamp":"2026-03-18T01:38:12.236Z","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/xpeng/Desktop/AiStudy/claude-learn/plugin-dev","sessionId":"95b3d4f4-8123-4885-9752-f1e600f4a1f6","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"frolicking-honking-lake"}
